PN,43402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1774861565
OL,3,CFirst British woman to win Olympic
OL,4,Cathletics gold dies aged 86
OL,6,FAfter gaining worldwide recognition
OL,7,Ffor her talent, she moved to
OL,8,FCalifornia.
OL,10,FThe City of Wells awarded her the
OL,11,FFreedom of the City in 2012. Speaking
OL,12,Fto ITV News, she said: "I'm truly
OL,13,Fhonoured. I'm really looking forward
OL,14,Fto seeing all the old friends that I
OL,15,Fhaven't seen since I was in school.
OL,17,F"I am really thrilled about the whole
OL,18,Fthing. I'll always feel a connection
OL,19,Fto Wells."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1774861565
OL,3,CFirst British woman to win Olympic
OL,4,Cathletics gold dies aged 86
OL,6,FShe added: "My heart will always be
OL,7,Fhere."
OL,9,FDuring a visit to Stoberry Park School
OL,10,Fthe same year, she explained: "I get
OL,11,Fvery nostalgic when I come over the
OL,12,FMendip Hills, having been gone in the
OL,13,FStates for as long as I have, it's
OL,14,Fnice to come back and be able to give
OL,15,Fback to the children.
OL,17,F"I especially enjoy that they can hold
OL,18,Fthe medals because not too many people
OL,19,Fever get a chance.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
